{"tid":2098002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派 35+ 公民投票 群眾集資!","createTime":"2020-07-07T07:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T14:18:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47bb153539665dd1a4556aa47f21df98beaf8626","tid":2098002,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"民主派 35+ 公民投票 群眾集資!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fdemocrats35plus%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=ae3803ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus/</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌方式及目標金額<br />\n<br />\n1 . 眾籌平台 (<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fdemocrats35plus&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=7dbf5437\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/democrats35plus</a>)<br />\n<br />\n2. 直接轉帳至民主動力的 恒生銀行戶口 (388-809709-001)，戶口名稱為 POWER FOR DEMOCRACY。<br />\n<br />\n**因選舉條例所限，請每位朋友捐款不多於港幣 1000 元**<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gogetfunding.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/6684994/img/fundraise_35+.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F6684994%2Fimg%2Ffundraise_35%2B.jpg&h=a5dfff52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資金運用計劃及項目比例分配<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事前宣傳 (各大傳媒、報章及網絡媒體與地區宣傳物資) &ndash; 80 萬港元<br />\n<br />\n投票程序、論壇及投票日行政、籌備、人手及運輸等安排 &ndash; 65 萬港元<br />\n<br />\n當日投票站場地(全港大約100 -150個)租金和設置，以及電子投票系統及器材等 &ndash; 180 萬港元<br />\n（依家實數係25x個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n事後民主派35+ 公民投票報告編撰及其他後續處理 &ndash; 5 萬港元<br />\n<br />\n眾籌平台及信用卡手續費 &ndash; 20 萬港元<br />\n<br />\n總計眾籌金額：350萬港元"},{"pid":"89a02de2b41f0b0051decdd73a05d99912f1b4b4","tid":2098002,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":6,"scor